## Cloudflare Pages ignore file
## Goal: Deploy only static frontend (HTML/CSS/JS/assets) and exclude backend, models, large artifacts, tests, infra configs.

### Exclude application backends / workers / orchestration
backend/
api-worker/
orchestrator/
model_server/
models/

### Exclude scripts and deployment helpers
scripts/
deploy/
setup_*.ps1
deploy_*.ps1

### Exclude Python environments & caches
.venv*/
venv/
env/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.egg-info/
*.cache/
cache/

### Exclude model + AI artifact file types
*.pt
*.onnx
*.ckpt
*.safetensors
*.bin
*.tar*
*.zip
*.7z

### Exclude infra / container / platform configs not needed by Pages
fly.toml
railway.json
docker-compose*.yml
Dockerfile*
nixpacks.toml

### Keep main README, ignore other heavy markdown docs
*.md
!README.md

### Exclude tests and test harness HTML/dev diagnostics
test_*.py
smoke_test*.py
test-*.html

### Exclude logs & env files
*.log
.env
.env.*

### Exclude git metadata
.git/
.gitignore

### Misc editor/temp files
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store

### Allow essential frontend assets explicitly (override broad patterns)
!assets/
!index.html
!mobile-index.html
!mobile-index-enhanced.html
!features.html
!about.html
!contact.html
!pricing.html
!signup.html
!login.html
